Different Types of Tables:

id - textalign - border -
1. Tables with border
2. Tables without borders
3. Tables without border with line under header
tr {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
}

4. without borders:
td,th{padding:6px;padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;border-left: 1px solid black;}th{border-bottom: 1px solid black;}table tr td:first-child,
table tr th:first-child {
  border-left: 0;
}td,th{padding:6px;padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;border-left: 1px solid black;}th{border-bottom: 1px solid black;}




5. irregular headers
    - remove first header and left most column be all bold
    - left most column be bold and spanning several rows, 2nd column be all bold and so on


